title: Statement by NSC Spokesperson Adrienne Watson on National Security Advisor Jake Sullivan’s Meeting with State Secretary for Foreign Affairs of Sweden Oscar Stenström | The White House
content: National Security Advisor Jake Sullivan met today with Oscar Stenström, State Secretary for Foreign Affairs to the Prime Minister of Sweden. Mr. Sullivan and Mr. Stenström discussed the security situation in Europe in light of Russia’s aggression in Ukraine, including their ongoing efforts to support Ukraine and impose costs on Russia. They committed to continue their close coordination on the full range of security issues.###
